data.description: Assumable mortgage at 2.250%! You can't beat this rate or even come close nowadays! This rate is available for this incredible home within walking distance to Heritage Elementary! This home boasts 5 bedrooms with all the extras. The windows have been tinted, security system installed, irrigation, covered deck, just to name a few of the adds to this home! This is one of the few homes with a view of the pond and no direct back yard neighbors! Call to set up a showing on this home today before its gone!  All information obtained from Seller and public records.
